snippet.textDisplay: I was 17 years old when I first heard your music and it came to me at the most perfect time it could. There had been a lot of hardships back then and your music just resonated with me. By 18 I had dyed blonde (group of us did a charity night where we all dressed as eminem and did a parody) after that I styled it like Chester's for a few months. Your music has always ment alot to me and many others. Just hate the fact I never got the opportunity to see you all live. My own fault as I made other things (alcohol and drugs) that I never should have a priority instead and that will always be a massive regret for me. Just want to say we love you all and thank you
